"{\"uid\": \"printweek.com-content-news-olympic-gold-medalist-visits-zerographic\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"\\\"Motivational and inspiring\\\"  Zerographic received a recent visit from Olympic canoe slalom gold medallist Joe Clarke MBE, who inspired the company's team members with his story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Jonas\", \"score\": 0.9984998872177763, \"rank\": 0.0008351074937813191, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Jonas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Jonas\"}, {\"begin\": 118, \"end\": 121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_the_British_Empire\", \"score\": 0.9999999999974989, \"rank\": 2.5893023453793845e-12, \"text\": \"MBE\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_the_British_Empire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_the_British_Empire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Stafford-headquartered kit reseller and Xerox Global Platinum Premium Partner has a close relationship with the athlete, who it sponsors.\", \"from\": 180, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 224, \"end\": 229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xerox\", \"score\": 0.9999927359306265, \"rank\": 7.264120903109479e-06, \"text\": \"Xerox\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xerox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xerox\"}, {\"begin\": 237, \"end\": 245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Music_recording_certification\", \"score\": 0.9983371152688807, \"rank\": 0.001461567205199987, \"text\": \"Platinum\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Music_recording_certification\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Music_recording_certification\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The business said that it was proud to support athletes who represent the country internationally and to encourage local talent.\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It said Clarke's visit served as a reminder of the positive impacts that business sponsorship could have on community development and sports.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke, who won a gold medal at the Rio 2016 Olympics and has been in preparation for the upcoming Paris 2024 Olympics, was warmly welcomed by the Zerographic team.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 631, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.603010878957805, \"rank\": 0.6582047471243544, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 635, \"end\": 648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 5.315470038890517e-13, \"text\": \"2016 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During his visit last month, he discussed his journey from humble origins to becoming an Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His story consisted of early\\u202fmornings, intense training sessions, and consistent support from his sponsors.\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His motivational speech shed light on the dedication required to succeed at the highest levels of competition.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He highlighted the value of teamwork in all areas of life, not only in sports, and drew comparisons between his own experiences and Zerographic's cooperative culture.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His ultimate message was that achievement is the result of perseverance, commitment, and a strong sense of community.\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke held an energetic Q&A session with the company's staff after his speech.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1400, \"end\": 1403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interview\", \"score\": 0.9999998355283559, \"rank\": 1.6447165368193442e-07, \"text\": \"Q&A\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interview\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interview\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Questions included everything from his training schedule and mental preparedness to his outlook on the future of British canoeing.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1568, \"end\": 1575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9998341388860854, \"rank\": 0.00015850174119938273, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He then thanked Zerographic for its ongoing support, emphasising how important its sponsorship was to his Olympic adventure.\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zerographic CEO Kevin Corbett told Printweek: \\\"Joe came and explained how much he had to commit and dedicate himself to the sport where he is now obviously an Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1729, \"end\": 1742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Corbett\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kevin Corbett\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Corbett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Corbett\"}, {\"begin\": 1748, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PrintWeek\", \"score\": 0.9999999878764357, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Printweek\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PrintWeek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PrintWeek\"}, {\"begin\": 1760, \"end\": 1763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Jonas\", \"score\": 0.9984998872177763, \"rank\": 0.0008351074937813191, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Jonas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Jonas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was good from a staff point of view because it's very motivational and inspiring, and it just goes to show that, ultimately, hard work is the ticket to success.\\\"\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 2056, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Following his Q&A, BBC Stoke interviewed Clarke regarding his feelings about the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2077, \"end\": 2080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.8076718667536027, \"rank\": 0.2379867447486006, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83d\\udde3\\ufe0f \\\"Quite an exciting period\\\"Stafford and Stone Canoe Club's@joeclarkek1says he's raring to go ahead of the Paris OlympicsHe'll be looking to add to his Gold medal from Rio 2016 \\ud83c\\udfc5\\ud83d\\udc4fpic.twitter.com/D4eogxCYIC  Zerographic employs 70 staff, with around 26 based at its headquarters and the remainder located across the UK.\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2270, \"end\": 2275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999417034376, \"rank\": 5.829647550876644e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Printweek Awards - Let them hear your ROAR!ThePrintweek Awardsare the highest profile awards scheme in UK print, celebrating business and production achievements across 18 categories.\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2669, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By entering you highlight your team's achievements and if you are shortlisted, highly commended or, fingers crossed, a winner you instantly raise your business's profile among clients and prospects and position it as a force in the industry throughout 2026.\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2927, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Printweek is the premier website for the print industry\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2932, \"end\": 2941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PrintWeek\", \"score\": 0.9999999878764357, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Printweek\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PrintWeek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PrintWeek\"}]}]}"